Habitat and Distribution. This species was found in soft substrata at depths ranging from 10 to 1000 m in the Sea of Marmara. It was previously reported on similar habitats between 6 and 1200 m depths in the Pacific Ocean (
León-González et al . 2006
), eastern Atlantic Ocean ( Aguirrezabalaga & Gil 2009 ) and the eastern (
Çinar et al . 2014
) and western ( Laubier 1971 ) Mediterranean Sea. This is the first report of the species from the Sea of Marmara.

